        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><span class="p fas fa-hashtag green"></span> 关于小白修改Volantis的一些配置</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="1-标签部件之添加公告"><a href="#1-标签部件之添加公告" class="headerlink" title="1. 标签部件之添加公告"></a><strong>1. 标签部件之添加公告</strong></h3><span class='p red'>位置(二选一)：</span><br>①volantis/_config.yml下的widget: 部分<br>②blog/source/_data/widget.yml<br><br><span class='p red'>代码：</span><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">announce:</span><br><span class="line">   class: text</span><br><span class="line">   display: [desktop,mobile]</span><br><span class="line">   header:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">     icon: fas fa-bullhorn</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">     title: 最新公告</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">     url:</span></span><br><span class="line">   content:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">     - </span>'写入内容'</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-导航栏之浏览页面时固定"><a href="#2-导航栏之浏览页面时固定" class="headerlink" title="2. 导航栏之浏览页面时固定"></a><strong>2. 导航栏之浏览页面时固定</strong></h3><span class='p red'>位置：</span><br>\volantis\layout\_pre.ejs 下的第8行<br>将此句<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">page.cover = theme.cover.display.others;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>删除或注释<br><span class='p cyan'>ps：在\volantis\layout\js\app.js中第48行开始，是关于页面中下移动时导航栏显示内标题的相关设置，可动也可不动</span></p><div class="note bug red">            <p>记得备份，不然头疼🤦‍♂️</p>          </div>]]></content>
      
      
      
